1. *Srčani* udar može biti vrlo opasan. (A *heart* attack can be very dangerous.)
2. Liječnici su utvrdili da ima problema sa *srčanim* zaliscima. (Doctors have determined that he has problems with his *heart* valves.)
3. *Srčana* aritmija je poremećaj srčanog ritma. (A *cardiac* arrhythmia is a disturbance of the heart rhythm.)
4. Najvažniji organ u tijelu je *srce* koje pumpa krv. (The most important organ in the body is the *heart* which pumps blood.)
5. Njegova majka je imala *srčani* udar prošle godine. (His mother had a *heart* attack last year.)
6. *Srčane* bolesti su vodeći uzrok smrti u mnogim zemljama. (*Cardiovascular* diseases are the leading cause of death in many countries.)
7. Ljubav prema glazbi bila je *srce* njegovog života. (The love of music was the *heart* of his life.)
8. Lijek koji uzima regulira *srčani* ritam. (The medication he takes regulates the *heart* rhythm.)
9. Nakon dugog trčanja osjetio je *srčani* udar. (After a long run, he felt a *heart* attack.)
10. Povremeno osjećam *srčanu* bol kada se uzbuđujem. (I occasionally feel *cardiac* pain when I get excited.)